Daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020, yawan kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin Turai ta Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai yana ƙaruwa cikin sauri.
Yawan adadin cututtukan cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) yana nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya, wanda ke tabbatar da cewa cutar COVID-19 ta duniya tana yaduwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe, duk da cewa tana da matakan daban-daban na ƙasa.
Bisa ga kwarewar Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da dakunan kula da lafiya na musamman suna buƙatar haɓaka shirye-shiryen su don tsammanin yawan marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa mai ƙarfi.
A ranar 31 ga watan Disamba na shekarar 2019, an samu rahoton wasu cututtukan cutar samba da ba a san dalilinsu ba a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, kasar Sin.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton cewa cutar ta haifar da cutar coronavirus ta hanyar Agent Novel, wanda ake kira cutar ta Coronavirus ta 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an sake kiran cutar ta coronavirus (COVID-19) da ke haifar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2.
Shaidar da aka samu har yanzu ta nuna cewa kashi 80% na marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 suna da wani abu mai tsanani, wato kamuwa da cutar numfashi tare da ko ba tare da cutar ba, kuma yawancin suna warkewa.
A cikin kashi 14% na masu cutar kansa, COVID-19 ya ci gaba zuwa matakin da ya fi tsanani kuma yana buƙatar yin asibiti, yayin da sauran kashi 6% na lokuta suna fama da mummunan ciwo wanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Kashi 4% na marasa lafiya da ke asibiti sun mutu saboda COVID-19.
A cikin wannan binciken, za mu kwatanta yanayin COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma a cikin Burtaniya (UK) da lardin Hubei na China.
A halin yanzu, mun kwatanta adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 a cikin EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya da waɗanda ke cikin Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
