A farkon watan Afrilu na shekarar 2020, masana kimiyyar CEPI sun ruwaito cewa dandamali daban-daban na fasaha 10 suna kan bincike da ci gaba don samar da allurar rigakafi mai tasiri akan COVID-19.
Babban burin dandamali wanda aka inganta zuwa Nazarin Tsaro na I ya haɗa da:
Nucleic acid (DNA da RNA) (mai haɓaka matakin I da mai neman allurar rigakafi Moderna, mRNA-1273)
Nau'in ƙwayar cuta (nau'in I na haɓakawa da rigakafi: Cancinobiology, nau'in adenovirus 5 vector)
A watan Afrilu na shekarar 2020, masana kimiyya sun ruwaito cewa, 'yan takarar allurar rigakafi 115 suna cikin matakai na farko na ci gaba, 78 sun bayyana cewa ayyukan suna aiki (79, a cewar Cibiyar Milken), kuma 37 sun bayyana, amma an kiyasta cewa bayanan da ke cikin jama'a ba su da yawa (a matakin shiri ko zane).
Gwajin Mataki na I-II yana gudanar da gwajin rigakafi na farko da amintacce, wanda galibi ana yin saurin kai, ana bincika shi a wuri kuma ana amfani da shi a wurare da yawa don ƙayyade mafi inganci da inganci.
Gwaje-gwaje na III sun haɗa da ƙarin mahalarta, waɗanda suka haɗa da ƙungiyoyin kulawa, tasirin maganin rigakafi, kuma sakamakon mummunan sakamako saboda an ba da sashi mai yawa.
