SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 sun riga sun yi amfani da su ta hanyar SARS-CoV saboda dukansu suna amfani da mai karɓar ACE2 don shiga cikin ƙwayoyin halitta.
Akwai hanyoyi uku na rigakafi da ake bincike.
Na farko, masu bincike suna da burin samar da allurar rigakafin cutar gaba ɗaya.
Ana amfani da wannan nau'in kwayar cutar, ko tana aiki ko ta mutu, don magance sabon haɗarin COVID-19 ga tsarin rigakafin mutum na mummunan cuta.
Hanyar ta biyu ita ce allurar rigakafi, wanda ake nufi da samar da allurar rigakafi da ke lura da tsarin rigakafin wasu ƙananan kwayoyin cutar.
A cikin yanayin SARS-CoV-2, irin wannan binciken ya mai da hankali kan furotin S-spike wanda ke taimakawa kwayar cutar ta dauki mai karɓar enzyme ACE2.
Hanyar uku ita ce yin allurar rigakafin nucleic acid (DNA ko RNA) don yin allurar rigakafi.
Dole ne a gwada alluran rigakafi na gwaji don aminci da inganci a cikin waɗannan hanyoyin. A ranar 16 ga Maris, 2020, an fara gwajin asibiti na farko na allurar a Seattle akan masu sa kai huɗu.
Allurar rigakafi tana da lambar halittar jini mara lahani daga kwayar cutar. An gabatar da shi a matsayin ingantaccen maganin rigakafin mutum don shirya rigakafin SARS-COV-2, amma wannan abu ne mai ban mamaki.
Tun daga watan Afrilu na 2020, an gudanar da gwajin asibiti sama da 300 a aiki.
A yanzu haka, ana nazarin hanyoyin da aka amince da su na cutar zazzabi, ciki har da bincike huɗu da aka amince da su, ciki har da bakwai na hydrochloroquine ko chloroquine.
Yawancin magungunan rigakafin da aka sake amfani da su suna gudanar da bincike na kasar Sin, wanda aka ruwaito a ƙarshen Afrilu a cikin gwaje-gwaje na Babi na III tara a cikin ƙasashe da yawa.
A watan Afrilu na shekarar 2020, an gudanar da bita mai canzawa kan ci gaban asibiti na allurar rigakafi da masu neman magani don COVID-19. Reflovir, chloroquine da hydrochlorokine, Lopeavia / Rutanavir da Lopenavir / Rudonavir tare da interferon beta suna nazarin yawancin magungunan riga-kafi na yanzu don maganin COVID-19 .
Akwai tabbaci na gaske game da tasirin rage farashin har zuwa Maris 2020.
A cikin asibiti, an sami ci gaba a cikin marasa lafiya da aka yi amfani da maganin jinƙai.
Ana gudanar da gwaje-gwaje na asibiti na mataki na III a Amurka, China da Italiya. An fara nazarin chloroquine a China a watan Fabrairun 2020.
Duk da haka, an yi kira ga masu bincike don yin nazarin.
Hukumomin kiwon lafiya na Koriya da na kasar Sin sun bada shawarar yin amfani da chloroquine.
Ko da yake, Cibiyar Kwayar cuta ta Wuhan ta ba da shawarar shan gram ɗaya a kowace rana, amma sau biyu na iya zama haɗari da kisa.
A ranar 28 ga Maris, 2020, Likitocin da ke kula da mutane da COVID-19 sun ba da izinin gaggawa don amfani da hydrochloroquine da chloroxine. Jagorar fitowar 7 ta kasar Sin ta kara da amfani da Interferon, ribavarin ko umfenovirine a kan COVID-19.
Bayanai na farko sun nuna cewa babban adadin ribavarin yana da mahimmanci don hana SARS-CoV-2 a cikin vitro.
Bayan nuna ƙananan matakan matsa lamba ga SARS-CoV-2, an ba da shawarar yin amfani da Nitazoxanide a cikin nazarin vivo. Nazarin ya nuna cewa, yana da mahimmanci don shigar da SARS-CoV-2 ta hanyar haɗuwa da babban amfani da furotin na trans-tissue protease serine 2 (TMPRSS2) tare da mai karɓar ACE2.
Nazarin da aka yi na chloroquine da hydrochloroquine tare da ko ba tare da arthromycin ba yana da manyan ƙuntatawa waɗanda ke hana al'ummar likitanci ɗaukar waɗannan magunguna ba tare da ƙarin bincike ba. Oseltamivir ba ya haifar da SARS-CoV-2 a cikin vitro kuma ba shi da wani muhimmin matsayi a cikin maganin COVID-19.
A cikin matakan COVID-19 na ƙarshe, hadari mai suna Cytoquin na iya zama mai rikitarwa.
Akwai hujja cewa hydroxychloroquine na iya samun halayen anti-cytocin. Tocilizumab an haɗa shi a cikin jagororin likita na Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa ta China bayan an kammala ƙaramin bincike.
A Italiya, ana gudanar da gwajin mataki na biyu a matakin ƙasa bayan ya nuna sakamako mai kyau a kan mutane da ke fama da mummunan cuta.
An yi amfani da shi don gano hadarin yutocin tare da gwajin jini na Sam Freistine, don hana irin wannan ci gaban da ake zaton zai haifar da mutuwar mutane da aka cutar.
An amince da FDA don interleukin-6 mai karɓar karɓa dangane da nazarin da aka buga a cikin CAR T cell therapy, a cikin 2017 dangane da amsawa ga maganin cututtukan fitowar isotonin steroidal.
Har zuwa yau, babu wani bayani na bazuwar da aka bincika game da yadda Tocalizim ke magance CRS.
Ana yin bincike kan yadda ake ba da allurar rigakafi ga mutanen da suka warke daga COVID-19 don neman maganin rigakafi da aka tace da kuma adanawa.
Wannan dabarar ta haifar da sakamako mara kyau ga kwarewar SARS.
Magungunan kashe ƙwayoyin cuta masu zaman kansu / masu zaman kansu sune matakan da aka tsara waɗanda zasu iya zama matsakaiciyar kariya akan SARS-CoV-2.
Duk da haka, akwai wasu hanyoyin da za a iya amfani da su, kamar su cytotoxic anti-addictive cell and / or phingyotosis.
Sauran hanyoyin magance rigakafin rigakafi na kai tsaye, kamar amfani da kwayoyin rigakafin monoclonal, suna da ƙarancin gaske.
Ana iya ƙara yawan ƙwayar cuta daga marasa lafiya da suka dawo daga cutar don saurin samar da ƙwayar cuta mai ƙwayoyin cuta na jini wanda ke ƙunshe da rigakafin cutar.
A cikin shekara ta 1914, an yi amfani da maganin cutar coronavirus a duniya.
